<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/east-west-railway-company> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The East West Railway Company is a non-departmental public arm’s length body set up by the government to accelerate the East West Rail project – a new rail link between Cambridge and Oxford. EWRC is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Transport ."@en .
